## Confidence Legend

- **HIGH** — ≥2 artifacts AND ≥1 test mapped, 0 hallucinated citations, all evidence types covered
- **MEDIUM** — ≥1 artifact OR ≥1 test mapped, 0 hallucinated citations, some evidence types missing
- **LOW** — Any evidence exists but coverage is weak or hallucinated citations detected
- **GAP** — No evidence mapped to this control

